Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AQUA為何會如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家為何會如此美好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為 大家都在心中收藏著美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 我還想繼續與更多的人邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 昨天的一場雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓今天的威尼斯披上了雪白的外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像為迎接即將到來的新年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給城市換上的新裝一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐 AQUA很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更深地去體會那裡夏日的炎熱和冬天的寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但AQUA實在太遠 我一個人無法前往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的新威尼斯 一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛 我過去也有過跟小愛一樣的想法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我 是那時的我想要成為的我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.29,0:01:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 差不多到時間去參加共同練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了 艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:39.23,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320,280)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那個 雪白的溫馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 藍華 香草茶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直溫暖到心裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這雪下得還真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個晚上就積了這麼厚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像新威尼斯城重生了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人害羞的台詞 禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽到「啊～」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 燈里小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 藍華 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.39,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們小時候想要變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.18,0:04:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.41,0:04:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是突然想到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能沒太想過這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小後輩還是小孩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我已經不是愛哭鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:04:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已經不是愛哭鬼了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標 果然還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像艾莉西亞前輩一樣的優雅女性啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又會被晃前輩罵的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.02,0:05:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為領航員的話 我還是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但艾莉西亞前輩還是我憧憬的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里前輩怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要變成艾莉西亞前輩那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學別人 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳可別小看了艾莉西亞前輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要變成那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要相當的努力和毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白嗎 毅力哦 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里妳沒有的吧 毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在想別的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 藍華
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩以前想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是個優雅的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我們去散步吧 燈里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,積了這麼厚的雪 大概不會有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就打烊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼出發啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又開始有點冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好暖和…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖包包 送給燈里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 燈里妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 這條路還沒有人走過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是第一名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩小時候想成為什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.84,0:08:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 叔叔也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾到這麼大應該夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不謝不謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那艾莉西亞前輩想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 不好意思 那個雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.45,0:09:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次滾這麼大的雪球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.99,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 我玩得非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上坡路很難滾呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的 要用力推哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺到哪都不會丟人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱鬧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我們馬上把它移走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.13,0:13:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不用不用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就放在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見到這麼大的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳們倆做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.05,0:13:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人都幫過忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那也讓我們來幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐們 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們就休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝點暖和的飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 好大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用 很暖和的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 純白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是白可可哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用白巧克力做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手一定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做三明治哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃點小蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也去幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要玩得太瘋喊腰痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說啥 這個不瘋怎麼行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要把它弄得更大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我們再多做一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 三彈嗎 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.19,0:15:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 剛才的領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.43,0:15:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經滾得這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也在幫忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那爸爸也再來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.11,0:15:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼幫忙啊 這本來就是領航員小姐的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領航員小姐真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了就用這個來裝飾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了 我還有些好看的布頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:16:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:16:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.65,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.38,0:17:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.28,0:17:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是滾雪球 卻能邂逅很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:51.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己被大家所溫暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越喜歡這個城市了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪的時候 我總是會去滾雪球玩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始滾雪球啊 總是會有人跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起幫我把雪球越滾越大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最後 大家都會很滿足地回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.89,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時侯啊 我突然想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想變成那樣的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個微笑 就如水之精靈一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這麼一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記了時間的流逝 看得入了迷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩果然是個美好的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉西亞前輩 謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳與我相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我這麼難能可貴的邂逅的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔地守護著我的這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里姐姐 我長大以後一定要去新威尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候燈里姐姐一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白的城市非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像艾莉西亞小姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 AQUA今天也很和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有在感謝本大爺嗎 鬢子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.12,0:20:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿帕爺爺 有人送了好吃的年糕給我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我也繼續在空中遨遊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要世界上還存在包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 藍華 我們去吃披薩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晃前輩請客嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可以考慮請妳吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 太好了 我去我去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.67,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 總有一天我會要妳加倍奉還
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妳成為正式領航員之後
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.49,0:22:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.80,0:22:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 天氣暖和起來後 我們去野餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密 不過是個很好的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.99,0:22:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那燈里想變成什麼樣的大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:23:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候想要成為精靈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.26,0:23:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 自由地在世界上飛舞 讓大家都得到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.48,0:23:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈里馬上也能成為精靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:46.23,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}希望 這座城市的溫馨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:48.89,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,0)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}能夠傳達到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.89,0:23:55.46,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1400,2400)\blur9\be1\fsp2\an2}許多人的心中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:02:04.49,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}窓からそっと 朝陽がのびて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:18.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}まどろむまつ毛に こぼれてくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:34.34,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}そよふく風 部屋へと招いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:47.79,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}木漏れ日に 君の寝顔 優しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:56.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつものありふれた朝だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:05.28,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}鮮やかに色づいてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:13.62,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}それは君と巡り合えた奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.22,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ひとりじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:25.26,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}君と一緒にいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OPCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:02:04.49,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}晨曦悄然漫入窗際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.62,0:02:18.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}灑落在 舒睡的睫毛間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:34.34,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}讓輕拂的風吹入小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:47.79,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}枝葉間滑落的陽光 映襯你的睡顏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.13,0:02:56.96,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雖是個平凡無奇的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:05.28,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}也染上了豔麗的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:13.62,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}那正是與你邂逅的奇蹟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:17.22,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:25.26,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}因為 有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDJP】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.84,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}手のひらの上に そっとのせた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:09.37,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}やさしさを あたためて そっと
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.21,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}口ずさんだ 秘密のメロヂィー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:21.24,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}歌ってよ 行くあてもないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.32,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}でも 降り出した雨も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:31.85,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}気にしない ずっとそばにいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:40.56,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.99,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:51.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:57.06,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:25.05,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いくつもの虹 越えて行けるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:28.72,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}ふたりで オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:36.38,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}小さな光 星に願いを
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:39.79,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}叶えてよ きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:47.54,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}描いてた夢 叶えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:50.87,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}いつかは オーバー ザ レインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:58.67,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}雨上がりの虹 見上げた空に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:04.61,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}はばたいて いつか 青い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:12.96,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}胸いっぱいの愛を 集めてよ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:19.73,OPEDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}心にはいつも愛を 越えてくわ きっとレインボー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【EDCH】
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:01.84,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}把悄然落在手心的溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:09.37,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}細細地 溫暖在懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:13.21,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}口中吟唱著神秘的曲調
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.59,0:20:21.24,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\an9}吟唱著 失去了方向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:25.32,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}可是 那飄落的雨滴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:31.85,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}卻不能影響我 因為有你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:40.56,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}穿過了 無數的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.99,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}我們 一起越過彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:51.67,OPEDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}一點微光 向星星許願
